# Engine Layer Rules

The engine layer contains core business logic and algorithms. It must remain independent of the app and presentation layers.

## Import Restrictions
- NEVER import from `apps/` or `presentation/`
- NEVER import from `runtime/` (engine is lower-level than runtime)
- OK to import from `shared/avrai_core`
- OK to import between engine packages (avrai_ai, avrai_ml, avrai_knot, avrai_quantum, reality_engine)

## Standards
- Use `developer.log()` from `dart:developer`, never `print()`
- Use `AppColors`/`AppTheme` for any color references (no direct `Colors.*`)
- All public APIs must have `///` doc comments
- All new scoring must use the energy function (Phase 4) or be flagged for future replacement
- Respect latency budgets: feature extraction < 50ms, state encoder < 20ms, energy function < 10ms
